<p>Gina Lanza Kane has been a licensed mental health counselor in the behavioral health field for over 30 years and is owner/operator of Compass Counseling Associates in Estero, Florida. Gina is a certified clinical supervisor, a national board certified counselor, and a disaster critical incident responder. Her primary specialty is providing therapy for the therapist and clinical supervisor, as well as discreet and private tele-health services. She is a graduate of Columbia University, University of Central Florida, and University of South Florida.</p>
